      <section eId="sec_1161">
        <num>1161</num>
        <heading>Eligible projects; priority ranking</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_1161__subsec_i">
          <num>(i)</num>
          <content>
            <p>public health and safety; (ii)\npopulation affected; (iii) attainment of state drinking water quality\ngoals and standards; (iv) taking into consideration the water resources\nmanagement strategy pursuant to title twenty-nine of article fifteen of\nthe environmental conservation law;</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1161__subsec_v">
          <num>(v)</num>
          <content>
            <p>taking into consideration future\nphysical climate risk due to sea level rise, and/or storm surges and/or\nflooding, based on available data predicting the likelihood of future\nextreme weather events, including hazard risk analysis data if\napplicable; and (vi) compliance with state and federal law, rules and\nregulations.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
